① The exam consists of 10 questions and you should answer all of them!
② You can only take one exam per course
③ Once you started the exam, you are not allowed to switch to another window or close it! If you did so your exam is cancelled and you will fail this course
④ You are allowed to use paper and pencil, nothing more!
⑤ The exam duration is 30 minutes, keep an eye on the timer.
⑥ Feel free to ask for your course instructor calrifications.
